precis:
Enactment of the NOTICE OF BRANCH CLOSURE (BANKS) REGULATIONS whereby banks
will be required to give four months' notice to its customers, the public
and to the Commissioner, prior to the closing of a branch located in an
urban area, and six months' notice in rural areas.
